text:
Mormons are a deeply traumatized people. All of us. Post, current, mainstream, offshoot.  And the only way to heal from generational trauma like this is to acknowledge that we perpetuate it, even without realizing it.

Leaving was hard. But staying was harmful.

Mormoni so globoko travmatizirani ljudje. Vsi mi. Nekdanji, sedanji, glavni, odcepljeni. Edini način za ozdravitev take generacijske travme je priznanje, da jo ohranjamo, tudi če se tega ne zavedamo.

Oditi je bilo težko. A ostati je bilo škodljivo.
